The paper deals with computational complexity of decision problems related to Nash equilibria in multi-player games, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT). The paper also uses techniques from computational complexity theory (cs.CC) and algorithms (cs.DS, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the complexity of decision problems related to symmetric Nash equilibria (cs.LG).
